It is used to give a sparse definition of an Interpretation as a list of PSymb. This definition assumed that symbols including in the list are considered True. The rest are considered False.

   -- i1 = {a=0, b=1}
   i1 =
       [ "b" ]

   -- i2 ={a=1, b=0}
   i2 =
       [ "a" ]

   -- i3 = {a=1, b=1}
   i3 =
       [ "a", "b" ]
